{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, ToG (Sun et al., 2024) uses the LLM to retrieve relevant facts hop-by-hop.",
    "RoG (Luo et al., 2024a) uses the LLM to generate plausible relation paths which are then queried on the KG to retrieve the relevant information, similar to semantic parsing.",
    "ToG utilizes an LLM to selectively expand and then prune the graph context.",
    "Meanwhile, RoG does not rely on any graph context.",
    "As a result, LLM-based approaches may overlook or incorrectly prune important graph information for KGQA tasks."
  ]
}